# Datacenter bootstrapping
# Create and configure hosts in this order
# 
# 1. fixion   -- the hypervisor host
# 2. ns1      -- and ns2 whenever later
# 3. dhcp
# 4. unifi    -- Wi-Fi AP controller software
# 5. freeipa  -- Can be done later but simplifies life
# 6. nginx    -- reverse-proxy
# 7. mysql and postgresql
# 8. web
# 9. the rest
